Source.Name: logseq
Source.Summary: A privacy-first, open-source platform for knowledge management and collaboration
Source.Description: Logseq is a knowledge management and collaboration platform. It focuses on privacy, longevity, and user control. Logseq offers a range of powerful tools for knowledge management, collaboration, PDF annotation, and task management with support for multiple file formats, including Markdown and Org-mode, and various features for organizing and structuring your notes.
